SEARCH
Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core

Class CloudSimTags

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.CloudSimTags
public class CloudSimTags extends Object
Contains various static command tags that indicate a type of action that needs to be undertaken by CloudSim entities when they receive or send events. NOTE: To avoid conflicts with other tags, CloudSim reserves negative numbers, 0 - 299, and 9600.
Since:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
Author:
Manzur Murshed, Rajkumar Buyya, Anthony Sulistio
